reviewText: If I could give more stars, I would! I love what Fit2B teaches you.  It's the foundation for life! I promise you won't regret it.  Beth, the women in the workout is real and truly connects with you in the videos.

I love Fit2B!  I used to have an online membership, which was great, but we decided to cancel our internet for a while, so I was so glad to be able to get this!  I use these exercises to help heal my diastasis, and they work great!  I love Bethany (the instructor); she is so encouraging!  My only complaint is that the formatting is a little off; the menu and such doesn't quite fit on my TV, but it's not really a big deal.
Perfect for addressing postpartum tummy issues.
Like it if I would only get past the first part after watching the first part I feel I can't do it right so have not moved on.
Love Bethany learn! She teaches in such a calm and easy manner.
Simple but very effective. I like it.
